<plot>An all new documentary called Anecdotes from EUROPA based on interviews with the cast and crew with an introduction by Peter Schepelern. Lars von Trier's closest collaborator and co-founder of Zentropa, Peter Aalbæk Jensen tells an amazing story about corpses and guns on the Autobahn in Germany. This is just one of the anecdotes from EUROPA.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?039685</url></doc>
